---
title: Shrimp Shawarma Pita Bar One recipe—endless ways to enjoy!
description: Our chef-curated “perfect plates” are the answer to your dinner woes! Set out a sumptuous Mediterranean-style spread of tender, garlicky shawarma-spiced dark meat chicken, fresh tomato-cucumber salad, zingy pickled onion, and warm pitas to wrap it all up, plus a creamy, tangy sauce for drizzling. Serve it all family style and order falafel and/or feta for even more choices!
